<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="delay-n">delay <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /dɪ'leɪ/    美 /dɪ'leɪ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u">1.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 耽误；延误；推迟：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Too many orders on 11th November caused a <strong>delay in</strong> delivery.
“双十一”订单太多，导致送货延期。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>After a long delay, the plane finally took off. 
在长时间的延误之后，飞机终于起飞了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Please send him the urgent information <strong>without delay</strong>.
请马上把这紧急的消息发给他。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>The World Health Organization gave a warning to the public without any <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (延误) when the virus of H1N1 hit Mexico in April, 2009.   （2009 福建改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. delay   </p></div>